--   gather_is_per_block_sliced, gather_is_deferred,
--   build_completes_without_abort, layer_output_via_single_path,
--   layer_output_via_block_path.
--
-- Test infrastructure to drive from this spec via allium:propagate:
--   - Property test that builds heterogeneous batches (varying
--     block shapes within one batch) and asserts
--     DtypeUniformAcrossBlocks and NoAbortOnContractedPatterns.
--   - Existing scripts/test-mtp-multislot.sh asserts at the
--     server level; the propagated test should sit at the
--     cgraph level (test-backend-ops style) so it reproduces
--     the bug deterministically without needing the 27B model.
